Title: UPenn Visual Perception and Memory Study (Please accept the HIT before beginning the experiment)
Description: This website contains a series of tests designed to assess your perception ability and memory for faces and colors. These tests are part of a research study at the University of Pennsylvania, conducted by the Aguirre Lab.
Keywords: memory, vision, UPenn, study, perception, experiment, face, color, test, task,
Answer.feedback2: Moving on and off the middle of the wheel changed the central face or color. This was confusing.
